name: A Creators Tale - Improvement
description:
There will be only one creation of this piece. If it is now yours, Congratulations. There is only one commitment required and that is that you pass it on once this particular journey or obstacle has been overcome for you.
There is only truth in your future. You have found a way to change. You have gained a firm understanding that change is inevitable and only works in your best interest. You have found your path. Walk it. Live it.
Hold these words in your mind, heart and daily thoughts.
